Brainsway Says High Frequency TMS Treatment Improved Alzheimer’s

-- B y   G w e n   A c k e r m a n
-- 
2011-09-27T07:14:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/brainsway-says-high-frequency-tms-treatment-improved-alzheimer-s.html
Brainsway Ltd. (BRIN)  said interim results
of a clinical test showed high frequency treatment with its
device for patients suffering from Alzheimer’s improved  their
condition. The company’s head researcher has recommended halting
tests using low frequency treatment following the results of the
test that was carried out in  Israel , the company said in a
statement to the Tel Aviv Stock Exchange today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gwen Ackerman in Jerusalem at 
 gackerman@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
